00:24:07.700 --> 00:24:09.980
biology disorders where there's not as obvious a phenotype-

402
00:24:10.240 --> 00:24:10.250
Yeah

403
00:24:10.250 --> 00:24:13.660
... what threshold do you think that people should then be considering the somatic

404
00:24:13.680 --> 00:24:14.080
reversion?

405
00:24:14.784 --> 00:24:18.024
So that's a really good question because somatic reversion is something that's only

