468
00:28:01.824 --> 00:28:04.364
screening. So a little bit about Lynch syndrome.

469
00:28:04.404 --> 00:28:07.964
It's the most common inherited GI cancer syndrome. It's autosomal dominant.

470
00:28:08.404 --> 00:28:11.604
The canonical cancers include colorectal and endometrial cancer.

471
00:28:12.184 --> 00:28:12.804
It's common.

472
00:28:13.824 --> 00:28:15.184
I'm going to say that again. It's common.

473
00:28:15.224 --> 00:28:18.664
Its prevalence is 1 in 350, similar to

474
00:28:18.704 --> 00:28:21.914
BRCA hereditary breast and ovarian cancer syndrome.

