00:30:03.864 --> 00:30:06.064
colorectal neoplasia incidence.

502
00:30:06.504 --> 00:30:10.124
And then very exciting studies that are underway, trials looking at

503
00:30:10.164 --> 00:30:12.964
immunoprevention and vaccines specific to Lynch

504
00:30:13.004 --> 00:30:16.974
syndrome.So these are the malignancies associated with

505
00:30:17.074 --> 00:30:20.754
Lynch. As you can see, they are numerous, and there's quite a variation between men

506
00:30:20.814 --> 00:30:23.574
and women, but also by the genotypes as shown here.

507
00:30:24.194 --> 00:30:27.954
Colorectal cancer, the most common, as well as

508
00:30:28.294 --> 00:30:32.254
endometrial. But as gastroenterologists, we're also very

509
00:30:32.334 --> 00:30:36.194
much aware of GI-associated malignancies for which we offer screening, including

