575
00:34:37.495 --> 00:34:41.435
So this is just in better understanding the magnitude

576
00:34:41.515 --> 00:34:43.515
of germline testing and cascade testing.

577
00:34:43.554 --> 00:34:47.435
If we had these two individuals both affected by colorectal

